OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777479067
OL,3,CFire rips through derelict former
OL,4,Cschool
OL,6,FThe roof of a Grade II listed derelict
OL,7,Fformer school in Dorset has collapsed
OL,8,Fafter a fire ripped through the
OL,9,Fbuilding.
OL,11,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService said crews were called to the
OL,13,Fblaze in the former independent
OL,14,Fschool, Newall House, in the Cornhill
OL,15,Farea of Sherborne, at approximately
OL,16,F6pm on Sunday 26 April.
OL,18,FFire chiefs said there were no
OL,19,Finjuries and the cause will be
OL,20,Finvestigated in due course.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
