PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777479067
OL,3,CFire rips through derelict former
OL,4,Cschool
OL,6,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService said around 35 firefighters
OL,8,Fwere sent to tackle the blaze at its
OL,9,Fheight.
OL,11,FCrews from Sherborne, Yeovil,
OL,12,FWincanton, Martock, Crewkerne and
OL,13,FChard attended, along with the aerial
OL,14,Fladder platform and a water carrier
OL,15,Ffrom Yeovil, and a command unit from
OL,16,FGillingham, the fire service added.
OL,18,FPeople living nearby were urged to
OL,19,Fkeep doors and windows closed due to
OL,20,Fthe large amount of smoke.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
