OL,3,CFire rips through derelict former
OL,4,Cschool
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Dorset and
OL,7,FWiltshire Fire Service said: "The
OL,8,Fbuilding's roof has collapsed, making
OL,9,Fthe structure even more unsafe.
OL,11,F"We still have two crews damping down.
OL,12,FThe fire investigator is due back on
OL,13,Fscene later this morning."
